<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link href="../css/out.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.min.js"></script>
  <title>Discord Bot Dashboard</title>
</head>

<body class="bg-transparent min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center">

  <div
    class="bg-gray-800/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-gray-700 p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full max-w-lg text-center animate-fade-in-up">

    <div class="mb-6">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation text-6xl text-red-500 mb-4"></i>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Ops! Algo deu errado.</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400">Não foi possível validar o canal ou a guilda solicitada.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 rounded-lg p-4 mb-8 text-left">
      <p class="text-sm text-red-400 font-mono">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info mr-2"></i>
        Erro: Canal de texto não encontrado ou sem permissão.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <button onclick="voltarAoDashboard()"
        class="bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-600 text-white font-semibold py-2.5 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors border border-gray-600 hover:border-gray-500">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left mr-2"></i> Voltar
      </button>
      <a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white text-sm font-semibold transition-colors">
        Suporte <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <script>
    function voltarAoDashboard() {
      window.history.back();
    }
  </script>
</body>

</html>